      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANNIHILATING (1) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing third last time beaten 5 lengths (20.21). Comes through a solid form race last start. Racing well and deserves a win. LOONGANA LILLY (8) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only a neck from the winner Royal Carol in second(17.40) at Casino. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Hard to beat again. SLIMY TROUT (2) finds it hard to break through. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when third (17.22) at Casino. Expected to be in this for a long way. ROCKY PEPPER (4) is worth consideration after filling a hole from the same draw last start.",
